an trung t\u00e2m CSKH Monkey Junior \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft, ch\u00fac b\u1ea1n ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi t\u1ed1t l\u00e0nh!&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=\&quot;text-align:justify;\&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/\&quot; rel=\&quot;dofollow\&quot;&gt;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&lt;\/a&gt; lu\u00f4n mong mu\u1ed1n cung c\u1ea5p cho b\u1ea1n nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch nh\u1ea5t cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n tham kh\u1ea3o th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean, h\u00e3y truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9! Ch\u00fac b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y t\u1ed1t l\u00e0nh v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y ni\u1ec1m vui. H\u1eb9n g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh Monkey Junior v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u0103ng k\u00ed M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t. C\u00e1ch li\u00ean h\u1ec7 t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t Monkey Junior. Xem ngay!&quot;,&quot;thumb_image&quot;:null,&quot;tags&quot;:null,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;huong-dan-dang-ki-khoa-hoc-monkey-junior-chi-trong-2-phut-moi-nhat&quot;,&quot;content_share&quot;:null,&quot;image&quot;:&quot;articles\/08-2022\/gGkCeFCeEe0mC3gnNgQqHvVYLJQ5jKRG1aTWOh2d.png&quot;,&quot;like&quot;:0,&quot;love&quot;:0,&quot;haha&quot;:0,&quot;wow&quot;:0,&quot;cry&quot;:0,&quot;angry&quot;:0,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;public&quot;,&quot;group_id&quot;:4,&quot;is_active&quot;:1,&quot;created_by&quot;:&quot;USER: #81&quot;,&quot;updated_by&quot;:&quot;ADMIN: #0&quot;,&quot;deleted_by&quot;:null,&quot;created_at&quot;:&quot;2022-08-02T03:13:46.000000Z&quot;,&quot;updated_at&quot;:&quot;2022-08-05T03:19:02.000000Z&quot;,&quot;deleted_at&quot;:null,&quot;parent_id&quot;:nu